3.5. Gas Chromatography Coupled to Flame Ionization Detector (GC-FID)

chromatograph (model 6890N) coupled to a ﬂame ionization detector (FID) and using a 7683 series
autoinjector (Agilent, Little Falls, DE, USA). The percentage composition of the oil was determined

but normalizing values with nonane as an internal standard. The qualitative analysis is expressed as
